      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Establishing a profile where material attributes are associated with a common material identifier (e.g. a number) for as many locations as possible.  This  will provide streamlined communication among the company’s locations, as well as to vendors for country, regional, or global RFQs.  Need to determine the logical scope for common materials.&#10;"/>
